name: Street Art
description:
In my opinion Street Art is a work of art that makes the street as its gallery. No need the invitation or be in a certain circle to be able to enjoy it. Every time I see street art, I am always amazed by their form and process. Since many Street Art works are made illegally, some results are good and some of them are mediocre.  

A tribute to Street Art. Because for me the street is a work of art itself. Respect!
